               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I did not take the money; his only suspicion was from my going away; he had used very brutal language to me the day before, which I did not like, and I went the next morning, took my things, and went away; he came and took me in charge; he took my coat, searched the pockets, and then threw the coat in my face; he saw the money taken from me, and that is the reason he can swear to it.</p>
